    "role": "Pragmatic Plumber / Sanitary Technician Applicant",
    "description": "A solid, no-nonsense tradesman in a grease-stained jacket and well-worn work boots. Arthur's face is weathered from years of leaning under sinks; his hands are callused and always smell faintly of pipe dope. He believes in physics and common sense, not corporate buzzwords. Motto: \"If it leaks, tighten it.\"",
